<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Welcome | Secure File Manager</title>
  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0f4f8, #d9e2ec);
      color: #333;
    }

    .header {
      padding: 60px 20px 40px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .header h1 {
      font-size: 2.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .header p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      color: #555;
    }

    .actions {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 40px;
      margin-top: 50px;
      padding-bottom: 80px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .card {
      background: white;
      padding: 30px 40px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      text-align: center;
      width: 300px;
      transition: transform 0.2s ease;
    }

    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
    }

    .card h2 {
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .card p {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: #666;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
    }

    .card a {
      display: inline-block;
      text-decoration: none;
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
    }

    .card a:hover {
      background-color: #0056b3;
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #777;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="header">
    <h1>Welcome to Secure File Manager</h1>
    <p>
      A safe, streamlined platform to upload, manage, and access your documents securely. Register today to experience secure file sharing and access from anywhere.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="actions">
    <div class="card">
      <h2>New Here?</h2>
      <p>Create your account to start uploading and organizing your files securely.</p>
      <a href="/user/register">Register</a>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h2>Already Registered?</h2>
      <p>Log in to your dashboard and access your uploaded files instantly.</p>
      <a href="/user/login">Login</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <footer>
    &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Secure File Manager. All rights reserved.
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
